measurements.description: One flower on one 36-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal flat, white, strongly marked green veins ; synsepal light green, darker green veins; petals spatulate, undulate, cream overlaid chartreuse basally, light rose distally, mahogany spots basal two-thirds; pouch light green, overlaid light rose, darker rose veins; staminode cream, green markings; substance firm; texture glossy.
